		{"id":"8a6db4554fc624d3","x":321,"y":89,"width":250,"height":60,"type":"text","text":""},
		{"id":"f18a90ce22b4d671","type":"text","text":"## 재현 시나리오\n\n- B: A를 공격 중\n- C: B를 추적 공격(더 빠른 도착)\n- B를 새 목적지로 이동 시도\n\n핵심 요구: B/C move_path_slot 동시 재계산","x":-540,"y":-1420,"width":360,"height":170,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"6c2e1b4890fa7d35","type":"text","text":"## StartMove\n\n입력 목표(req*)와\n분기 보정(resolved*) 확인\n\n`[TroopTrace][StartMove:*]`","x":80,"y":-1405,"width":280,"height":140,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"2fbd3079e4a8c651","type":"file","file":"04. Work/AN Games/Analysis/Troop_Manager_StartMove_UpdateAttacker_Analysis.md","x":-40,"y":-940,"width":520,"height":360},
		{"id":"a3b2c1d0e9f8a7b6","type":"text","text":"## TroopLOD 분석 맵\n\n핵심 엔트리: `SetTroopSlotData()`\n\n함수군을 6개 책임으로 분리:\n- 라이프사이클/편성\n- 유닛생성/LOD/애니메이션\n- 이동/회전/경로\n- 선택/타겟마크\n- 전투 이펙트\n- DTO 동기화 파이프라인","x":-560,"y":1060,"width":560,"height":320,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"b4c5d6e7f8091a2b","type":"file","file":"04. Work/AN Games/Analysis/TroopLOD_Function_Analysis_Index.md","x":60,"y":1060,"width":560,"height":360},
		{"id":"f4a8c7d1b3e29065","type":"file","file":"04. Work/AN Games/Analysis/NetworkTroop_UpdateAttacker_Analysis.md","x":-560,"y":-1200,"width":560,"height":360,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60781","type":"text","text":"## 3057/3051 레이스 컨디션\n\nupdateTargetUser에서 로컬 갱신된\n공격자 데이터를 Phase 5의 3057이\nstale 서버 데이터로 덮어쓰는 버그\n\nUserList에 공격자 user_no 추가로 해결","x":-560,"y":-720,"width":420,"height":200,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"b2c3d4e5f6078192","type":"file","file":"04. Work/AN Games/Analysis/UpdateAttacker_3057_RaceCondition_BugFix.md","x":0,"y":-720,"width":560,"height":360,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"1d2f9a7be6c44a11","type":"text","text":"## Firebase Manager\n\n초기화 / Analytics / Crashlytics / FCM\n\niOS 안전 종료 상태머신 포함","x":1940,"y":20,"width":420,"height":180,"color":"4"},
